title: Mass nickname changer (rewrite only)
description: This cog lets you change/reset everyones nickname on a server at once.

commands.massnick|mn [onlineonly] [new nickname]: Apply [new nickname] to the all users. [onlineonly] can be either true or false.
commands.resetnicks|rn: Removes nicknames from all users on the current guild.

author: Bluscream#2597
